[99.4, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u2713 no duplicate anchoring; cursor resumed.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[101.8, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m\u2500\u2500 9 \u00b7 F6/U2/R2 \u00b7 the reusable document-indexer module\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[106.8, "o", "\u001b[2mupload\u2192storage_module (codex cid), broadcast\u2192delivery_module, dedup+retry. self-contained crate.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ grep -nE 'storage.upload|delivery_module.*send|StorageBackend::LogosCore' document-indexer/src/lib.rs | head -3\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[109.2, "o", "88:/// `storage_module` (Codex-backed, via the `agent_module` `storage.upload`\r\n89:/// skill proven in LP-0008) and `delivery_module` (`send`), through the\r\n107:        StorageBackend::LogosCore {\r\n"]
[109.5, "o", "\u001b[1;32m$ cargo test -p document-indexer --lib 2>&1 | grep 'test result'\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[111.9, "o", "test result: ok. 3 passed; 0 failed; 0 ignored; 0 measured; 0 filtered out; finished in 0.05s\r\n"]
[114.3, "o", "\u001b[1;32m\u2713 indexer wired to real Logos modules; dedup + retry tested.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
